<a href="http://tdfsc.files.wordpress.com/2011/07/developers.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-631 " title="Number of developers" src="http://tdfsc.files.wordpress.com/2011/07/developers.png?w=422&amp;#038;h=210" height="210" alt="Number of developers" width="422"></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Number of developers</p>
