<div id="post-344173" class="blog-post position-6 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/libreoffice/blog/more-than-24-hours-to-go%E2%80%A6">More than 24 hours to go…</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">24 de Julho de 2011, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/libreoffice/blog/more-than-24-hours-to-go…#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><p>…since we have just extended the deadline for sending in papers for the LibreOffice Conference. You can now <a href="http://conference.libreoffice.org/submit-your-paper/">send in your proposals</a> until August 8th!</p>
